59 /* glcorearb.h is for use with OpenGL core profile implementations.
60 ** It should should be placed in the same directory as gl.h and
61 ** included as <GL/glcorearb.h>.
62 **
63 ** glcorearb.h includes only APIs in the latest OpenGL core profile
64 ** implementation together with APIs in newer ARB extensions which
65 ** can be supported by the core profile. It does not, and never will
66 ** include functionality removed from the core profile, such as
67 ** fixed-function vertex and fragment processing.
68 **
69 ** Do not #include both <GL/glcorearb.h> and either of <GL/gl.h> or
70 ** <GL/glext.h> in the same source file.
71 */
72

1473 #ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1474 /* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
1475 #define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1476 /* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
1477 /* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
1478 #if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
1479 #include <inttypes.h>
1480 #elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
1481 #include <inttypes.h>
1482 #if defined(__STDC__)
1483 #if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
1484 typedef long int int64_t;
1485 typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
1486 #else
1487 typedef long long int int64_t;
1488 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1489 #endif /* __arch64__ */
1490 #endif /* __STDC__ */
1491 #elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
1492 #include <inttypes.h>
1493 #elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
1494 #include <stdint.h>
1495 #elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
1496 typedef long int int32_t;
1497 typedef long long int int64_t;
1498 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1499 #elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
1500 #include <stdint.h>
1501 #elif defined(_WIN32)
1502 typedef __int32 int32_t;
1503 typedef __int64 int64_t;
1504 typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
1505 #else
1506 /* Fallback if nothing above works */
1507 #include <inttypes.h>
1508 #endif
1509 #endif
